title: CudaMiner 2014-02-28 nVidia Mining Software (for Windows, Linux)
description:
CudaMiner, nVidia mining software. Please use cgminer for ATi cards. Use CPUminer for CPU mining.

Supports scrypt, scrypt-jane, keccak and other algorithms.

Required dependencies for building on Windows:
pthreads
OpenSSL-Win32
curl-7.29.0


Linux compilation is also possible now:
chmod +x configure autogen.sh     (.zip does not preserve the x bit)
./autogen.sh && ./configure && make
